{"tid":881241,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU決心私下匯錢！2度收私訊遭詐騙⋯真相讓她超受傷","createTime":"2018-10-29T09:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T08:43:48.000Z","uid":34643,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4576a51a8206d666653c6cec5f4c44ee6cf52ca1","tid":881241,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:42:34.000Z","msg":"南韓女歌手IU年紀輕輕出道，唱紅許多經典夯曲，出道10年站穩人氣solo女歌手的位置。人美心也善的她每年都會固定公益捐款，27日出演談話性節目《對話的喜悅》，提及自己捐款的契機，其實是曾經遭留言給她的粉絲受騙，讓她決定幫助其他真正需要幫助的人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3652/d3652848.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3652%2Fd3652848.jpg&h=db660377&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲IU私訊中，有很多事請她匯錢幫忙的訊息。（圖／翻攝自KBS）<br />\n<br />\nIU出道滿10年，出演談話性節目《對話的喜悅》分享一路走過來的道路，她的歌曲走療癒路線，同樣也是粉絲的心靈導師，Instagram時常收到粉絲的苦惱商談信件，其中還包含網友表示經濟困難、拐個彎向她要錢，從醫藥費、學費，欠債等大筆金額都有。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3652/d3652850.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3652%2Fd3652850.jpg&h=1ff80c81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲IU下定決心幫助一位私訊網友，沒想到對方是騙子。（圖／翻攝自KBS）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3652/d3652849.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3652%2Fd3652849.jpg&h=17cc03e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲IU二度收到私訊，對方表示希望她再多匯一點錢，結果被她發現該名網友根本在騙人。（圖／翻攝自KBS）<br />\n<br />\n「我一定要幫助這位。」該名網友幾個月以來不斷傳訊息給她，讓IU下定決心幫助一名素未謀面的粉絲，真的把錢匯給對方，後來她收到感謝的訊息，但該名網友貪婪地表示「可不可以再匯多一點錢給我」。IU從此以後沒再回該位網友的訊息，幾天後，她發現該名網友換了一個帳號，繼續向她要錢。<br />\n<br />\nIU發現自己受騙的當下，「當時真的很受傷。」但也是因為如此，她決定每年固定捐款，幫助真正需要幫助的人。"},{"pid":"d4be9502b09b6f447f020b391b18faa6168080aa","tid":881241,"uid":3303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:43:13.000Z","msg":"IU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd1c90bc6ea966d5fbaaf1dd72c7d9b8243e543","tid":881241,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:44:07.000Z","msg":"觀音下凡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce4af72d74faacc56cbcd4f3a134e857f01c089","tid":881241,"uid":213300,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:44:34.000Z","msg":"港女=豬西<br />\nIU=人善被人欺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b015c2ea695f01125da359a339f4ccb5931a6ee2","tid":881241,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d136be32c5bdf9a8f909d9e9ddae24a2a06ee6a","tid":881241,"uid":109655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cce4af72d74faacc56cbcd4f3a134e857f01c089","tid":881241,"uid":213300,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:44:34.000Z","msg":"港女=豬西<br />\nIU=人善被人欺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:06:36.000Z","msg":"靚女做乜都係啱嘅<br />\n何況重要係IU<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19467e61bf757d0cb651c46322b10b581b3c3378","tid":881241,"uid":56230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:07:49.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係騙色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c0ce54280ba778db5bcd69212a9242c1d96062","tid":881241,"uid":14797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe63fcb840dac5af3a1f4a15a39b1078c9ba81f5","tid":881241,"uid":41394,"like":3,"disl